1.title: Kuponová privatizace
1.plot: Peter Malina teaches Karel and his colleagues how to behave like real businessmen. Majda and her mother Zuzka go to a cottage, because they have to learn. Tonda does not feel well because of the bankruptcy of the public house. Zuzka meets Sean. She knows that she has feelings for him. Jarda and his father are successful with privatization. Iveta finally publishes a colorful magazine for the travel agency. But then, her father and her sister appear.

2.title: Au-pair
2.plot: Karel deals with issues in the company. Jarda meets his father's new secretary. Tonda starts working in FBIS, where he meets Kabelka. Zuzka resists Sean's love pressure.
